100
00:10:46,370 --> 00:10:47,800
our Beiyang Army

101
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:49,570
has established a tradition.

102
00:10:50,010 --> 00:10:51,580
Every time we have a major drill,

103
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:53,800
