110
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:08,930
Isn't this pandering to foreign customs?

111
00:11:08,930 --> 00:11:10,130
Indeed.

112
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:13,120
Come, come, let's drink.

113
00:11:13,170 --> 00:11:14,050
Tell me.

114
00:11:14,370 --> 00:11:16,370
Is all this Western stuff that good?

115
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:18,370
It's not all that special, is it?

116
00:11:19,490 --> 00:11:21,100
Let's talk about this steak.

117
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:23,690
Not to mention the gaminess,

118
