121
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:29,460
What's so good about it?

122
00:11:31,090 --> 00:11:32,350
Listen up, General Li,

123
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,370
you should stop complaining.

124
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:36,190
You pick up your plate to eat with such vigor,

125
00:11:36,190 --> 00:11:37,720
but you start cursing as soon as you are done.

126
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,170
That's not fair of you.

127
00:11:40,070 --> 00:11:40,870
Let me ask you.

128
00:11:41,370 --> 00:11:43,720
After the Western dinner in Zhangde was over,

129
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,680
who was it that took

130
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:45,700
the restaurant's knives and forks,

131
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:48,630
stuffed it into their pockets, and then took it home?

132
00:11:49,940 --> 00:11:51,570
Wait, there's more.

133
00:11:52,050 --> 00:11:53,320
He didn't even spare

134
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,930
the small knives and forks

135
00:11:54,930 --> 00:11:56,730
for spreading butter and fruit.

136
00:11:57,130 --> 00:11:57,800
It's made of silver.

137
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,860
So they were worth quite a bit, right?

138
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:01,800
Did that happen?

139
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,930
I don't remember.

140
00:12:04,250 --> 00:12:05,010
General Li.

141
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:06,130
Do you really not remember,

142
00:12:06,130 --> 00:12:07,320
or are you pretending not to?

143
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:07,930
Yeah.

144
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:09,480
Come on, let's drink.

145
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,530
Come on, come on.

146
00:12:11,130 --> 00:12:12,190
Let's not talk about it anymore.

147
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:12,830
Kaizhi,

148
00:12:13,430 --> 00:12:14,580
