184
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,720
All participating units

185
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,410
are to return to their original stations immediately

186
00:14:04,410 --> 00:14:05,870
and await further orders.

187
00:14:06,250 --> 00:14:07,050
Do not

188
00:14:08,170 --> 00:14:09,370
act rashly.

189
