206
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,440
I didn't expect the autumn military drill

207
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:47,100
to end just as it was starting.

208
00:15:49,250 --> 00:15:50,860
You all go ahead with your work.

209
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:51,790
I have something

210
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:54,070
