Hurry up, hurry up!

212
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:16,320
Kaizhi.

213
00:16:18,130 --> 00:16:19,560
Since we met in Shanghai,

214
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:22,970
we've stayed close for over 10 years.

215
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:27,010
And actually, all the trials and tribulations of the past 10 years

216
00:16:27,010 --> 00:16:28,670
have been leading up to today.

217
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,740
Why do you say that?

218
00:16:34,050 --> 00:16:35,170
I have to say it.

219
00:16:37,930 --> 00:16:39,630
The severity of the situation in Wuhan

220
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:40,880
is much worse

221
00:16:41,330 --> 00:16:43,060
than what I've conveyed to you.

222
00:16:44,130 --> 00:16:44,800
