225
00:16:48,130 --> 00:16:49,590
My head is full of numbers.

226
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:52,040
These numbers are telling me

227
00:16:52,130 --> 00:16:53,060
that our country

228
00:16:53,890 --> 00:16:55,600
is in the danger of collapse.

229
00:16:58,130 --> 00:16:59,190
Is it that serious?

230
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,770
From what I understand,

231
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:03,680
Hubei’s treasury has amassed

232
00:17:03,680 --> 00:17:05,569
a fortune of over 10 million yuan.

233
00:17:06,369 --> 00:17:07,240
Now, that has completely

234
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:09,240
fallen into the hands of the rebels.

235
00:17:09,369 --> 00:17:10,500
That amount of money

236
00:17:11,410 --> 00:17:12,440
is more than enough to buy

237
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:15,099
the loyalty of the entire lower Yangtze region.

238
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,099
Not to mention,

239
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,440
Hanyang hosts the biggest

240
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:19,200
munition factory in the nation.

241
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:20,440
The arsenal in Wuchang

242
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,609
originally stored

243
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:22,609
