244
00:17:22,609 --> 00:17:24,089
purchased from Germany,

245
00:17:24,970 --> 00:17:26,450
15,000 Type 65 rifles

246
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,540
bought from Japan,

247
00:17:28,329 --> 00:17:29,480
plus tens of thousands of rifles

248
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:31,880
produced by the Hanyang munition factory.

249
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,040
Together with mountain guns, field artillery,

250
00:17:33,040 --> 00:17:34,300
and fortress cannons,

251
00:17:34,610 --> 00:17:36,330
such a massive amount of weaponry

252
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:37,960
is enough for the rebels to

253
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:40,090
expand their forces by five brigades within 3 days.

254
00:17:40,090 --> 00:17:40,960
Therefore,

255
00:17:41,610 --> 00:17:42,770
if the court wants to suppress

256
00:17:42,770 --> 00:17:44,230
the rebellion in Wuchang,

257
00:17:44,570 --> 00:17:47,370
they must deploy the main forces of the Beiyang Army.

258
00:17:47,370 --> 00:17:48,030
Otherwise,

259
00:17:48,810 --> 00:17:50,040
there's no other way.

260
00:17:56,130 --> 00:17:56,930
I understand.

261
00:17:58,850 --> 00:18:00,110
What you are saying is,

262
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:02,330
the Sixth Division is returning to its station

263
00:18:02,330 --> 00:18:03,930
so that we can be redeployed.

264
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,130
Rest assured,

265
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:08,380
after my Sixth Division returns to our station,

266
00:18:08,570 --> 00:18:10,770
we'll be ready for your orders, Tufang.

267
00:18:11,850 --> 00:18:13,110
That's hard to say now.

268
00:18:13,610 --> 00:18:14,680
At this moment,

269
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,720
the cabinet ministers are deciding on who shall be

270
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:19,380
the Beiyang commander to lead the troops south.

271
00:18:19,610 --> 00:18:21,010
Prince Qing has asked for

272
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,330
Yuan Shikai

273
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:24,180
to come out of retirement.

274
00:18:25,570 --> 00:18:26,440
Yuan Shikai...

275
00:18:26,810 --> 00:18:28,200
coming out of retirement?

276
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:28,930
I've already sent a telegram

277
00:18:28,930 --> 00:18:30,330
expressing my willingness

278
00:18:30,330 --> 00:18:31,570
to volunteer to lead the troops south.

279
00:18:31,570 --> 00:18:32,570
But the possibility of being appointed

280
00:18:32,570 --> 00:18:33,630
is extremely slim.

281
00:18:34,850 --> 00:18:35,810
That's why I sent an urgent message

282
00:18:35,810 --> 00:18:36,680
to Lord Zaitao,

283
00:18:36,850 --> 00:18:38,960
urging him to tell the Prince Regent that

284
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,220
even if I am not chosen,

285
00:18:40,570 --> 00:18:41,950
Yuan Shikai must not be allowed

286
00:18:41,950 --> 00:18:43,410
to come out of retirement.

287
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:51,610
It really seems like a critical moment.

288
00:18:51,610 --> 00:18:52,270
Therefore,

289
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,010
for the Sixth Division,

290
00:18:54,230 --> 00:18:55,230
Lord Zaitao and I

291
00:18:55,610 --> 00:18:57,210
can only rely on you, Kaizhi.

292
00:18:57,910 --> 00:18:59,630
We can trust no one else.

293
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:03,680
Just watch.

294
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:06,830
Once Yuan Shikai comes out of retirement,

295
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:08,890
Brigade Commander Wu and Li Renjun

296
00:19:09,090 --> 00:19:11,750
will naturally become his staunch supporters.

297
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:15,440
Tufang.

298
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:17,920
To be honest with you,

299
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:19,680
just now,

300
00:19:20,930 --> 00:19:22,240
it already feels as if

301
00:19:23,020 --> 00:19:25,150
I’m walking a tightrope among wolves.

302
00:19:28,570 --> 00:19:29,330
To be frank,

303
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:31,090
Kaizhi,

304
00:19:32,570 --> 00:19:33,570
in my eyes,

305
00:19:34,610 --> 00:19:36,200
aren't you a wolf as well?

306
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:44,090
You must be joking.

307
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,330
I'm serious.

308
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:50,500
Then make yourself clear.

309
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:53,200
What kind of wolf am I?

310
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,400
You know it yourself.

311
00:19:57,850 --> 00:19:58,780
No, I don't know.

312
00:20:01,090 --> 00:20:01,950
Even if you are,

313
00:20:02,330 --> 00:20:03,130
you're a wolf that has been

314
00:20:03,130 --> 00:20:05,190
dancing closely with me for 10 years.

315
00:20:12,370 --> 00:20:13,330
Don't laugh.

316
00:20:15,090 --> 00:20:16,200
I advise you, Yang Kaizhi,

317
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:18,000
to continue to remain rational.

318
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:20,080
Do you understand?

319
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:34,310
[Sixth Division's Field Command]

320
00:21:35,330 --> 00:21:36,040
The Wuchang Uprising

321
00:21:36,040 --> 00:21:37,720
has caused a tremendous shock.

322
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,040
Many young officers

323
00:21:39,090 --> 00:21:40,570
are as excited as if they've been

324
00:21:40,570 --> 00:21:41,970
injected with morphine.

325
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:45,240
Excitement alone is not enough.

326
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:49,040
Are they willing to sacrifice for the revolution?

327
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:55,720
I'm confident I can win over

328
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,700
Feng Hanhai's 24th Regiment.

329
00:21:57,930 --> 00:21:58,720
Kaizhi.

330
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:00,760
If you can also persuade Renjun,

331
00:22:00,810 --> 00:22:03,610
then the entire Twelfth Brigade will be complete.

332
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:07,330
I think the biggest trouble is the Eleventh Brigade.

333
00:22:07,330 --> 00:22:08,200
That man, Wu,

334
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:11,040
is stubborn and unyielding.

335
00:22:12,370 --> 00:22:14,330
Then let's work from the bottom up.

336
00:22:14,810 --> 00:22:16,370
First, we'll mobilize a few junior officers

337
00:22:16,370 --> 00:22:18,040
with revolutionary leanings.

338
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:19,330
Then we'll disarm Wu.

339
00:22:20,330 --> 00:22:21,440
After that, we'll announce

340
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:25,170
the reorganization of the Eleventh Brigade's command structure.

341
00:22:25,370 --> 00:22:27,100
Seems like that's the only way.

342
00:22:27,850 --> 00:22:29,910
The key is to choose the right timing.

343
00:22:32,080 --> 00:22:32,880
Let's do this.

344
00:22:33,370 --> 00:22:34,240
You immediately send

345
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:35,970
a few trusted comrades to Wuhan

346
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:37,960
and establish contact with

347
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,120
the revolutionary forces.

348
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:40,580
Okay, I'll get right on it.

349
00:22:51,990 --> 00:22:52,480
Report!

350
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:54,220
Brigade Commander Li has arrived.

351
00:22:54,220 --> 00:22:54,620
Enter.

352
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:58,850
Kaizhi.

353
00:23:00,090 --> 00:23:02,090
Something doesn't seem right to me.

354
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,200
What's not right?

355
00:23:04,330 --> 00:23:05,680
I just came from the station.

356
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:06,610
The railway folks told me that

357
00:23:06,610 --> 00:23:07,480
according to the transport plan,

358
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:09,630
the 20th Division and the 2nd Mixed Brigade

359
00:23:09,630 --> 00:23:11,490
are both staying put in Luanzhou.

360
00:23:12,570 --> 00:23:14,030
What are they trying to do?

361
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:17,850
Is that so?

362
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,330
Is that what's happening?

363
00:23:21,330 --> 00:23:21,810
Report!

364
00:23:21,930 --> 00:23:22,610
A telegram from General Liang Xiang

365
00:23:22,610 --> 00:23:25,010
of the Beijing Military Advisory Council.

366
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:26,940
Read it.

367
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,330
The cabinet ministers have decided that

368
00:23:29,330 --> 00:23:31,090
Minister of the Army Yinchang will lead as commander-in-chief

369
00:23:31,090 --> 00:23:32,200
and lead the main forces of the Beiyang Army south

370
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:33,470
to quell the rebellion.

371
00:23:33,470 --> 00:23:34,440
Your Eleventh Brigade is to be

372
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:35,930
immediately incorporated into the 2nd Army,

373
00:23:35,930 --> 00:23:37,200
and follow them south under the command of

374
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,000
Sir Yinchang.

375
00:23:40,330 --> 00:23:40,930
It's over.

376
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,440
The telegram is signed off by

377
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:43,640
General Liang Xiang.

378
00:23:48,570 --> 00:23:50,370
What about our Twelfth Brigade?

379
00:23:50,370 --> 00:23:52,830
Should we continue to return to our station?

380
00:23:59,850 --> 00:24:01,930
This is my reply to General Liang Xiang.

381
00:24:01,930 --> 00:24:03,530
As the Sixth Division's commander,

382
00:24:03,530 --> 00:24:05,590
I, Yang Kaizhi, requests permission

383
00:24:05,850 --> 00:24:08,330
to personally lead the Eleventh Brigade

384
00:24:08,850 --> 00:24:10,510
to the frontlines of Wuchang.

385
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:17,170
Has it been sent?

386
00:24:17,330 --> 00:24:19,190
Yes, Commander. It has been sent.

387
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:19,960
Come!

388
00:24:20,090 --> 00:24:20,570
Here!

389
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,480
Notify Brigade Commander Wu

390
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:28,330
that the movement of the Eleventh Brigade has changed.

391
00:24:28,330 --> 00:24:30,090
Have them rest at the original station

392
00:24:30,090 --> 00:24:31,370
and be on stand by for my orders.

393
00:24:31,370 --> 00:24:31,900
Yes, Sir!

394
00:24:45,570 --> 00:24:46,030
Report!

395
00:24:46,090 --> 00:24:49,290
A reply telegram from Sir Yinchang at the Ministry of War.

396
00:24:51,850 --> 00:24:52,310
Read it.

397
00:24:52,570 --> 00:24:54,440
Your Eleventh Brigade should load up where you are,

398
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,720
then head towards Kaifeng in Henan to gather

399
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:56,850
and report to the 2nd Army.

400
00:24:56,850 --> 00:24:57,720
Your request, Commander Yang,

401
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:58,680
bears commendable spirit.

402
00:24:58,680 --> 00:24:59,560
If you insist so,

403
00:24:59,560 --> 00:25:01,330
you may report to my Headquarters.

404
00:25:01,330 --> 00:25:01,960
The Eleventh Brigade

405
00:25:01,960 --> 00:25:03,470
remains under the command of Brigade Commander Wu.

406
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:04,330
This telegram is signed off by

407
00:25:04,330 --> 00:25:06,130
Minister of the Army, Yinchang.

408
00:25:26,370 --> 00:25:27,130
Qianli,

409
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,640
it seems that we brothers

410
00:25:32,090 --> 00:25:33,550
are on the same path again.

411
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:36,240
That's right.

412
00:25:36,930 --> 00:25:38,610
One division has only two brigades.

413
00:25:38,610 --> 00:25:39,850
If you don't personally lead the Eleventh Brigade,

414
00:25:39,850 --> 00:25:40,960
what are you there for?

415
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:42,740
Even if you end up at the General Headquarters,

416
00:25:42,740 --> 00:25:44,470
you'll just be a staff officer.

417
00:25:50,850 --> 00:25:51,570
Qianli.

418
00:25:52,810 --> 00:25:54,200
Help me analyze this.

419
00:25:57,090 --> 00:25:58,330
The higher-ups

420
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:00,290
always want to clip

421
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:02,070
my wings as Yang Kaizhi.

422
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:06,650
They're determined to separate me from my own troops

423
00:26:06,720 --> 00:26:08,350
as the division commander,

424
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:13,190
Why is that?

425
00:26:20,760 --> 00:26:25,890
[Zhengyang Gate Station, Beijing]

426
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:27,610
Wulou.

427
00:26:28,770 --> 00:26:31,100
You are a bearer of great responsibility.

428
00:26:31,540 --> 00:26:33,890
The safety of the court depends on you.

429
00:26:35,610 --> 00:26:36,410
Seventh Lord,

430
00:26:36,650 --> 00:26:38,310
I understand what's at stake.

431
00:26:38,510 --> 00:26:39,660
But your brother...

432
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:42,140
seems to still be overly anxious.

433
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:44,310
For state and military matters,

434
00:26:44,330 --> 00:26:45,090
haste can do

435
00:26:45,820 --> 00:26:46,950
more harm than good.

436
00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:48,330
I understand.

437
00:26:48,610 --> 00:26:49,570
As for the Prince Regent,

438
00:26:49,570 --> 00:26:51,620
I will take care of everything for you.

439
00:26:51,620 --> 00:26:56,850
[Commander-in-chief to the south, Minister of the Army, Yinchang]

440
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:53,680
Tufang,

441
00:26:54,360 --> 00:26:55,960
we still need to be careful of

442
00:26:56,270 --> 00:26:58,000
those from the Sixth Division.

443
00:26:59,040 --> 00:27:00,040
Yang Kaizhi?

444
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,640
I made a slight probe,

445
00:27:02,720 --> 00:27:04,480
and that person immediately backed off.

446
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:05,720
He never mentioned about

447
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:07,320
going to Wuchang ever again.

448
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:11,810
If it were me, I wouldn't do it either.

449
00:27:11,810 --> 00:27:13,050
Why would I leave my position as commander

450
00:27:13,050 --> 00:27:15,310
only to become your subordinate, right?

451
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:17,850
How could I possibly

452
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:19,930
let him lead troops to Wuchang?

453
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:21,510
Wouldn't that be like releasing

454
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:22,970
a turtle back into the sea?

455
00:27:26,570 --> 00:27:28,370
It's not that serious, isn't it?

456
00:27:29,610 --> 00:27:30,950
We should still be cautious.

457
00:27:30,950 --> 00:27:32,350
After all, he still has

458
00:27:32,530 --> 00:27:34,460
command over the Twelfth Brigade.

459
00:27:34,610 --> 00:27:35,330
Moreover,

460
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:37,820
it's right in the capital region.

461
00:27:38,970 --> 00:27:40,100
Don't worry, Wulou.

462
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,200
I'll strip him of

463
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,730
his military powers later.

464
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,220
Tufang,

465
00:27:45,860 --> 00:27:46,780
find a reason.

466
00:27:59,590 --> 00:28:06,290
[Shanghai]

467
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:08,330
Read the news! Read the news!

468
00:28:08,330 --> 00:28:09,440
Read about how the Hubei Military Government,

469
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:10,480
Governor Li Yuanhong,

470
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,930
has sent a telegram to the whole country

471
00:28:11,930 --> 00:28:14,240
announcing the liberation of the three towns of Wuhan.

472
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,610
Read the news! Read the news!

473
00:28:15,610 --> 00:28:16,370
One newspaper, please.

474
00:28:16,370 --> 00:28:16,970
Yes, sure.

475
00:28:17,570 --> 00:28:18,960
Read the news! Read the news!

476
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:20,810
Read about how the court's Minister of the Army, Yinchang,

477
00:28:20,810 --> 00:28:25,010
is leading the main forces of the Beiyang Army south to quell the rebellion.

478
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:45,240
Yingshi,

479
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:47,280
Troops are raised over years to be used in a moment of need.

480
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,600
Is your merchant militia up to the task?

481
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:50,010
Let's talk inside.

482
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,610
Send the snacks over.

483
00:28:55,810 --> 00:28:56,680
Come, come.

484
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:58,090
Hurry, hurry up. Keep up.

485
00:28:58,610 --> 00:28:59,960
Have some fruit.

486
00:29:01,130 --> 00:29:02,200
Concubine Song, you're working so hard.

487
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:03,680
Not at all, it's what I should do.

488
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:04,330
Hua,

489
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:06,340
quickly refill the tea.

490
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,240
Alright.

491
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,090
I'm back.

492
00:29:30,090 --> 00:29:30,620
Let's go.

493
00:29:39,810 --> 00:29:40,740
What's going on?

494
00:29:41,090 --> 00:29:42,890
It's like a bustling market day.

495
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:44,130
I don't have a single familiar face.

496
00:29:44,130 --> 00:29:45,730
Don't ask so many questions.

497
00:29:46,490 --> 00:29:47,850
I have been a law-abiding

498
00:29:47,850 --> 00:29:48,740
citizen all my life.

499
00:29:48,740 --> 00:29:49,940
I've had enough of it.

500
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,370
With the thunderous uprising in Wuchang,

501
00:29:52,370 --> 00:29:54,100
the time of awakening has come.

502
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:55,090
Those hibernating underground,

503
00:29:55,090 --> 00:29:56,360
like insects and toads,

504
00:29:56,360 --> 00:29:58,490
are bound to awaken and stir things up.

505
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,130
Why are they all dressed like you,

506
00:30:01,130 --> 00:30:03,130
wearing merchant militia uniforms?

507
00:30:03,130 --> 00:30:04,680
You're not going to fight, are you?

508
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,610
We've been in training hard

509
00:30:05,610 --> 00:30:06,960
in Pudong for almost two years

510
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:07,960
all for this day.

511
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:09,960
Not bad, you.

512
00:30:10,850 --> 00:30:12,680
If a man can’t make his mark,

513
00:30:12,930 --> 00:30:14,790
what’s the use of his strong body?

514
00:30:16,130 --> 00:30:17,130
So in other words,

515
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:19,460
Shanghai is about to respond to Wuchang?

516
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,540
It's been decided.

517
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:22,240
We'll liberate Shanghai by force.

518
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:24,240
You came back at just the right time.

519
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:26,850
So...

520
00:30:27,330 --> 00:30:28,730
have you seen your lover?

521
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:29,820
How's Kaizhi?

522
00:30:30,210 --> 00:30:31,010
Who told you?

523
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:34,230
You disappoint me.

524
00:30:34,980 --> 00:30:36,660
Why can't you see my worth?

525
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,200
I'm really hurt.

526
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,440
Truly hurt.

527
00:30:39,890 --> 00:30:40,400
Tell me,

528
00:30:40,610 --> 00:30:42,390
you didn't fancy me back in Anqing.

529
00:30:42,390 --> 00:30:44,390
Fine, I've been working hard since.

530
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:46,580
I've attended Japanese military school

531
00:30:46,580 --> 00:30:48,480
and participated in armed revolution.

532
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:49,870
Why you still can't see my worth?

533
00:30:49,870 --> 00:30:50,600
Quit joking.

534
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:51,480
No.

535
00:30:52,090 --> 00:30:53,610
You need to explain yourself.

536
00:30:53,610 --> 00:30:55,170
How am I not good enough?

537
00:30:56,040 --> 00:30:58,610
Isn't he just the commander of the Sixth Division?

538
00:30:58,610 --> 00:31:00,190
His rank is only slightly higher than mine

539
00:31:00,190 --> 00:31:02,200
and has a few more men under his command.

540
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,440
What's the big deal?

541
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:04,130
My potential

542
00:31:04,130 --> 00:31:05,790
is no less than Yang Kaizhi's.

543
00:31:07,850 --> 00:31:08,570
Tell me,

544
00:31:08,590 --> 00:31:10,260
where can I find Huang Keqiang?

545
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,090
I need to report to him

546
00:31:11,090 --> 00:31:14,420
on the progress of the Sixth Division in the capital region.

547
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,660
I'm afraid you won't find him.

548
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:22,730
You're really putting on airs now, Song Chen.

549
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:25,330
Huang Xing left for Wuchang the day before yesterday.

550
00:31:25,330 --> 00:31:26,200
He has already established

551
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:28,090
the Central Headquarters of the Chinese Alliance.

552
00:31:28,090 --> 00:31:28,960
Now,

553
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,810
you're under my leadership.

554
00:31:30,810 --> 00:31:31,570
You?

555
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:33,110
Why can't I lead you?

556
00:31:33,810 --> 00:31:35,480
There are thousands of people in the merchant militia.

557
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:36,810
I trained them all.

558
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:38,500
I'm the chief drillmaster.

559
00:31:38,500 --> 00:31:39,480
I'm just not as good as

560
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:41,520
Lin Chong, the chief instructor of 800,000 royal guards.

561
00:31:41,520 --> 00:31:42,780
Alright, stop joking.

562
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:44,040
Let's be serious.

563
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:46,130
What arrangements did your father make?

564
00:31:46,130 --> 00:31:47,200
I was just joking.

565
00:31:48,810 --> 00:31:50,680
Can women truly handle firearms?

566
00:31:51,660 --> 00:31:53,570
Even if you could, I wouldn't let you do it.

567
00:31:53,570 --> 00:31:55,100
Can you be serious for once?

568
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,090
Fine.

569
00:31:56,610 --> 00:31:57,440
I'll go get your leader

570
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:59,040
to come and assign you a task.

571
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:01,780
Show him some respect.

572
00:32:02,090 --> 00:32:04,130
This old man has a big appetite for power.

573
00:32:04,130 --> 00:32:04,960
He has now become

574
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:05,850
the Finance Minister

575
00:32:05,850 --> 00:32:07,450
of the Alliance in Shanghai.

576
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:32,880
What are you laughing at?

577
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:34,530
Your attire...

578
00:32:34,650 --> 00:32:36,630
really makes you look like a finance minister.

579
00:32:36,630 --> 00:32:38,290
Don't you listen to Song Chen.

580
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:41,180
Am I the type of person who wants to be an official?

581
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:42,040
If I really wanted to be an official,

582
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:43,860
I would have done it in the 21st year of Guangxu.

583
00:32:43,860 --> 00:32:45,060
Why wait until today?

584
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:47,240
How is Kaizhi?

585
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:48,750
When we parted,

586
00:32:48,850 --> 00:32:50,200
I didn't expect the situation

587
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:51,460
to develop so quickly.

588
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,200
So...

589
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:54,370
I'm afraid the original situation...

590
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:58,520
I just received news at noon.

591
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:02,440
Among the Beiyang Army participating in the autumn military drill,

592
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:03,440
the 20th Division

593
00:33:03,610 --> 00:33:05,200
and the 2nd Mixed Brigade

594
00:33:05,610 --> 00:33:07,410
have refused the court's orders

595
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:10,380
and jointly caused trouble in Luanzhou, Hebei.

596
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:11,330
Is that so?

597
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:13,610
What about Kaizhi's Sixth Division?

598
00:33:13,610 --> 00:33:14,330
No news yet.

599
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,530
What do you need me to do?

600
00:33:19,610 --> 00:33:20,930
My current workplace is at

601
00:33:20,930 --> 00:33:22,130
the Ningbo Chamber of Commerce.

602
00:33:22,130 --> 00:33:23,200
Come with me.

603
00:33:23,220 --> 00:33:24,350
I need an assistant.

604
00:33:26,370 --> 00:33:27,200
Shuhong.

605
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:29,370
Shanghai will respond to Wuchang

606
00:33:29,370 --> 00:33:30,700
to achieve liberation.

607
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:33,530
There are many things waiting for us to do.

608
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:46,310
[Military Advisory Council]

609
00:33:47,370 --> 00:33:48,440
As to Zhang Shaozeng

610
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:50,040
and Lan Tianwei's relatives in Beijing,

611
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,370
we must treat them well.

612
00:33:51,570 --> 00:33:52,900
We must not harass them.

613
00:33:53,170 --> 00:33:54,090
After all, the 20th Division

614
00:33:54,090 --> 00:33:55,040
and the 2nd Mixed Brigade

615
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:57,040
haven't taken any extreme actions.

616
00:33:57,090 --> 00:33:58,490
We need to give them time.

617
00:33:58,570 --> 00:33:59,870
Don't push them too hard.

618
00:33:59,870 --> 00:34:01,480
If pushed too far, they might really rebel.

619
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:02,540
Whose idea is this?

620
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,090
Of course, it's Lord Zaitao's

621
00:34:04,090 --> 00:34:05,150
personal opinion.

622
00:34:05,370 --> 00:34:06,170
He's gone out.

623
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:08,020
I have full authority to represent him.

624
00:34:08,020 --> 00:34:10,420
Yes, I am representing him fully.

625
00:34:15,330 --> 00:34:16,210
Tufang,

626
00:34:17,210 --> 00:34:19,080
are you being this lenient

627
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,639
because these two

628
00:34:20,639 --> 00:34:22,969
were your fellow officer cadets in Japan?

629
00:34:25,250 --> 00:34:27,600
They neither return to their garrisons at Fengtian

630
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:29,030
nor head south to quell the rebellion.

631
00:34:29,030 --> 00:34:30,050
Instead, they sent telegrams to the court

632
00:34:30,050 --> 00:34:31,250
demanding a constitutional monarchy.

633
00:34:31,250 --> 00:34:32,639
This is a military remonstration!

634
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:33,900
It's a serious matter.

635
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:35,989
Lord Zaitao,

636
00:34:36,989 --> 00:34:38,260
I think you are only seeing half the picture

637
00:34:38,260 --> 00:34:39,659
and is missing the whole.

638
00:34:40,210 --> 00:34:40,960
Have you figured out

639
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,250
what's the most serious aspect

640
00:34:42,250 --> 00:34:43,650
of this whole situation?

641
00:34:45,210 --> 00:34:46,080
I'm listening.

642
00:34:46,810 --> 00:34:49,639
The mantis stalks the cicada, unaware of the oriole behind.

643
00:34:49,639 --> 00:34:51,040
The most dangerous place

644
00:34:51,120 --> 00:34:53,250
is neither in Wuchang nor in Luanzhou,

645
00:34:53,530 --> 00:34:54,989
but in Huanshang Village.

646
00:34:57,210 --> 00:34:58,340
Huanshang Village?

647
00:34:58,970 --> 00:34:59,830
That guy, Yuan?

648
00:34:59,930 --> 00:35:00,730
That's right.

649
00:35:01,370 --> 00:35:02,640
It's him, Yuan Shikai.

650
00:35:10,300 --> 00:35:11,100
Tufang.

651
00:35:12,250 --> 00:35:13,810
In times of crisis like now,

652
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:16,320
we can't dwell on past grievances.

653
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:18,430
That's too...

654
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:19,620
Lord Zaitao.

655
00:35:20,640 --> 00:35:21,600
At this point in the game,

656
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:23,200
haven't you realized it yet?

657
00:35:24,790 --> 00:35:25,590
Indeed.

658
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:29,160
As soon as news of the Wuchang Uprising broke,

659
00:35:29,160 --> 00:35:30,890
the entire court was in chaos like headless flies.

660
00:35:30,890 --> 00:35:32,550
There was no clear consensus.

661
00:35:32,930 --> 00:35:35,190
That's why on the day Yinchang departed,

662
00:35:35,560 --> 00:35:36,710
Feng Guozhang, who was going to battle,

663
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:39,040
made a special trip to Huanshang Village.

664
00:35:39,410 --> 00:35:40,740
What does that signify?

665
00:35:40,970 --> 00:35:43,160
Of course, it was to seek guidance on strategy.

666
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:45,690
The big decisions still had to come from Yuan.

667
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,840
What happened next was strange.

668
00:35:48,890 --> 00:35:50,420
It's been several days now,

669
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:51,440
and the vanguard

670
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:53,120
still hasn't entered Hubei.

671
00:35:54,160 --> 00:35:55,420
Where is Yinchang now?

672
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,470
Still on the train in Xinyang.

673
00:35:58,690 --> 00:35:59,890
Is our Minister of the Army

674
00:35:59,890 --> 00:36:02,290
out for a stroll or actually fighting a war?

675
00:36:03,370 --> 00:36:04,160
Oh right.

676
00:36:07,300 --> 00:36:08,340
I'm puzzled too.

677
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:10,740
What are these people waiting for?

678
00:36:10,740 --> 00:36:13,040
Isn't it obvious what they're waiting for?

679
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:14,640
The entire main force of Beiyang who is heading south

680
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:15,690
has shown a level of inaction

681
00:36:15,690 --> 00:36:17,890
completely inconsistent with their strength.

682
00:36:17,890 --> 00:36:19,490
One can only understand that

683
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:20,560
they are waiting for a

684
00:36:20,560 --> 00:36:21,960
new commander to appear.

685
00:36:23,250 --> 00:36:24,250
Are you saying...

686
00:36:25,850 --> 00:36:27,440
They're waiting for Yuan Shikai?

687
00:36:27,440 --> 00:36:28,080
If not, why do you think

688
00:36:28,080 --> 00:36:30,110
Prince Qing nominated for Yuan to come out of retirement?

689
00:36:30,110 --> 00:36:32,310
Was it really just a desperate measure?

690
00:36:40,330 --> 00:36:40,730
Hello?

691
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:43,440
Your Highness, it's me.

692
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:47,930
Seventh Lord is here. Please wait a moment, Your Highness.

693
00:36:49,030 --> 00:36:50,670
Zaifeng, it's me.

694
00:36:51,730 --> 00:36:53,130
Go ahead, I'm listening.

695
00:36:55,550 --> 00:36:56,070
What?

696
00:37:00,340 --> 00:37:01,140
I understand.

697
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:08,060
What did His Highness say?

698
00:37:08,690 --> 00:37:10,330
You actually called it.

699
00:37:11,210 --> 00:37:12,940
The edict has just been issued,

700
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:15,120
requesting Yuan Shikai to come out of retirement

701
00:37:15,120 --> 00:37:16,050
in order to serve

702
00:37:16,050 --> 00:37:17,510
as the Viceroy of Huguang.

703
00:37:18,720 --> 00:37:20,780
Isn't this letting the tiger back in?

704
00:37:22,490 --> 00:37:23,290
This won't do.

705
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:26,930
I must go talk to His Highness personally.

706
00:37:27,210 --> 00:37:28,330
We absolutely cannot give Yuan Shikai

707
00:37:28,330 --> 00:37:29,790
full military authority.

708
00:37:58,960 --> 00:37:59,850
Viceroy Liang.

709
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,220
Hurry up, hurry up!

710
00:38:32,890 --> 00:38:33,640
Quickly!

711
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:37,100
Be careful not to fall.

712
00:38:40,250 --> 00:38:41,120
Hurry, hurry!

713
00:38:41,340 --> 00:38:42,400
Keep up at the back.

714
00:39:09,160 --> 00:39:11,090
Your Highness, your meal is ready.

715
00:39:11,930 --> 00:39:13,130
Is Tufang still here?

716
00:39:13,730 --> 00:39:15,460
Ask him to come and dine with me.

717
00:39:15,810 --> 00:39:16,370
Yes, Sir.

718
00:39:39,410 --> 00:39:40,270
Your Highness.

719
00:39:40,330 --> 00:39:41,990
Sit down, let's eat together.

720
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:53,100
I heard from Seventh Lord...

721
00:39:56,730 --> 00:39:57,600
that you seem to have something

722
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:58,410
to tell me.

723
00:39:59,660 --> 00:40:01,720
Perhaps it's better not to say it now.

724
00:40:05,810 --> 00:40:06,440
Why?

725
00:40:08,640 --> 00:40:10,640
I didn't expect things to change so quickly.

726
00:40:10,640 --> 00:40:13,440
The situation has taken a sharp turn for the worse.

727
00:40:14,890 --> 00:40:15,890
It seems...

728
00:40:16,780 --> 00:40:18,840
the telegraph war has already begun.

729
00:40:21,930 --> 00:40:22,810
Telegraph war?

730
00:40:24,790 --> 00:40:25,920
Yes, telegraph war.

731
00:40:27,580 --> 00:40:28,560
Since the widespread use of telegraphs

732
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:29,730
in the Qing dynasty,

733
00:40:30,530 --> 00:40:31,410
this is the first time

734
00:40:31,410 --> 00:40:33,820
it has become a powerful tool in the hands of rebels.

735
00:40:33,820 --> 00:40:34,950
Using the telegraph

736
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,490
and starting from Wuchang,

737
00:40:37,730 --> 00:40:39,790
they unleased the rebellion's cause

738
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,040
rampantly

739
00:40:41,040 --> 00:40:43,040
across the country like a plague.

740
00:40:44,090 --> 00:40:46,380
Next would be Hunan, Shaanxi,

741
00:40:46,490 --> 00:40:48,930
Jiangxi, Shanxi, and Yunnan.

742
00:40:50,530 --> 00:40:51,490
I estimate that

743
00:40:52,160 --> 00:40:53,210
other provinces will

744
00:40:53,210 --> 00:40:54,340
eventually join in.

745
00:40:55,370 --> 00:40:56,830
Its speed of transmission

746
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:59,520
is the same as that of the telegraph.

747
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,520
There are too many fish bones.

748
00:41:06,780 --> 00:41:07,700
Take it away.

749
00:41:25,820 --> 00:41:26,570
Carry on.

750
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:31,560
The root of the issue lies in this one "ko" move.

751
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:35,370
"Ko"?

752
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,900
The lone "ko" move left on a shattered board.

753
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:43,840
You mean the three towns of Wuhan?

754
00:41:44,790 --> 00:41:45,460
Yes,

755
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:47,970
the three towns of Wuhan

756
00:41:48,330 --> 00:41:50,260
are exactly the biggest pain point

757
00:41:50,890 --> 00:41:53,150
between me and the revolutionary party.

758
00:41:54,730 --> 00:41:55,530
You're right.

759
00:41:57,600 --> 00:41:59,250
What troubles me the most

760
00:42:00,750 --> 00:42:02,500
is this "ko".

761
00:42:06,310 --> 00:42:10,530
The revolutionary party has been searching for five or six years, hasn't it?

762
00:42:10,530 --> 00:42:12,190
They've always wanted to find

763
00:42:13,250 --> 00:42:15,180
a "ko" that could fight against us.

764
00:42:18,490 --> 00:42:19,820
Xu Xilin in Anqing,

765
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:21,730
Qiu Jin in Shaoxing,

766
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:24,840
Huang Xing in Guangzhou.

767
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:27,820
They were looking out,

768
00:42:29,250 --> 00:42:30,080
but all of them

769
00:42:30,870 --> 00:42:32,400
failed to form a stalemate.

770
00:42:33,410 --> 00:42:34,610
Without a stalemate,

771
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:38,240
a "ko" cannot be formed.

772
00:42:43,330 --> 00:42:44,640
But this time in Wuhan,

773
00:42:47,160 --> 00:42:48,270
they've found it.

774
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:53,330
If Wuhan becomes

775
00:42:53,330 --> 00:42:54,810
China's Bastille,

776
00:43:00,250 --> 00:43:01,250
then all the

777
00:43:02,960 --> 00:43:04,820
latent crises of the Qing dynasty

778
00:43:06,640 --> 00:43:08,480
may be triggered

779
00:43:08,480 --> 00:43:09,640
by this "ko".
